@startuml

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #495057
    ArrowColor #495057
    FontColor #212529
}
skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    BorderColor #6C757D
}
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #495057
    ArrowColor #495057
    FontColor #212529
    DiamondBackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    DiamondBorderColor #495057
}
skinparam swimlane {
    BorderColor #6C757D
    TitleBackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    TitleFontColor #212529
    TitleFontSize 13
}
skinparam ArrowColor #495057
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F0C000

title Pipeline Execution\n<size:11><color:#6C757D>pipeline() helper orchestrating sequential processing stages via GeneratesText trait</color></size>

|GeneratesText|
start
:Caller invokes **TextProvider::prompt(AgentPrompt $prompt)**;
:Generate UUID invocation ID\n<size:10>Str::uuid7()</size>;
:Create **pipeline()** instance\n<size:10>Illuminate\\Pipeline\\Pipeline(Container::getInstance())\n.send($prompt).through($middleware).then($callback)</size>;

|Middleware Assembly|
:Initialize empty middleware stack;

if (Agent is faked?\n<size:10>Ai::hasFakeGatewayFor(agent)</size>) then (yes)
  :Prepend **fake-recording middleware**\n<size:10>Ai::recordPrompt()</size>;
else (no)
endif

if (Agent uses **RemembersConversations** trait\n+ hasConversationParticipant()?) then (yes)
  :Append **RememberConversation** middleware;
else (no)
endif

if (Agent implements **HasMiddleware**?) then (yes)
  :Append agent's own **middleware()** array;
else (no)
endif

|GeneratesText|
note right
  Assembled middleware stack
  is passed to .through()
end note

:Pipeline executes middleware chain **sequentially**;

repeat
  :Middleware receives **AgentPrompt**\n<size:10>can read / transform prompt, attachments, model</size>;
  :Middleware calls **$next($prompt)**\nto pass control to next stage;
repeat while (More middleware?) is (yes)
-> no, all middleware passed;

note right
  RememberConversation wraps
  $next() — stores conversation
  data **after** the response returns
end note

:**Terminal callback** invoked;
:Store **processedPrompt** reference;
:Dispatch **PromptingAgent** event\n<size:10>(invocationId, prompt)</size>;

if (Agent implements **Conversational**?) then (yes)
  :Load **agent->messages()** as\nconversation history base;
else (no)
  :Use **empty []** as messages base;
endif

:Append **UserMessage**(prompt text, attachments)\nto messages array;
:Register tool event listeners\n<size:10>listenForToolInvocations(invocationId, agent)</size>;

if (Agent implements **HasStructuredOutput**?) then (yes)
  :Build **JSON schema**\n<size:10>agent->schema(JsonSchemaTypeFactory)</size>;
else (no)
  :Set **$schema = null**;
endif

|TextGateway|
:Call **textGateway()->generateText(**\n  provider, model, instructions,\n  messages, tools, schema,\n  TextGenerationOptions::forAgent(agent), timeout\n**)**;

:Send request to **LLM API**;

repeat
  :Receive LLM response chunk / message;
  :Accumulate into **Step** or **StructuredStep**\n<size:10>text, finishReason, usage, meta</size>;
  if (Response contains **tool call**?) then (yes)
    :Dispatch **InvokingTool** event\n<size:10>assign currentToolInvocationId</size>;
    :Execute tool, capture result;
    :Dispatch **ToolInvoked** event\n<size:10>with tool result</size>;
    :Append tool result to messages\nand re-submit to LLM;
  else (no)
  endif
repeat while (LLM requests more tool calls?) is (yes)
-> no, final text response received;

:Return **GatewayResponse**\n<size:10>text, structured?, toolCalls[], toolResults[],\nsteps[], usage, meta, messages[]</size>;

|GeneratesText|
if (**$schema** is not null?\n<size:10>structured output requested</size>) then (yes)
  :Build **StructuredAgentResponse**\n<size:10>new StructuredAgentResponse(\n  invocationId, structured, text, usage, meta)\n  .withToolCallsAndResults(...)\n  .withSteps(steps)</size>;
else (no)
  :Build **AgentResponse**\n<size:10>new AgentResponse(\n  invocationId, text, usage, meta)\n  .withMessages(messages)\n  .withToolCallsAndResults(...)\n  .withSteps(steps)</size>;
endif

|ConversationStore|
if (Agent uses **RemembersConversations**?) then (yes)
  if (Agent has **no** currentConversation()?) then (yes)
    :Generate **conversation title**\n<size:10>textGateway()->generateText(cheapestTextModel)\n→ 3–5 word summary of prompt</size>;
    :**store->storeConversation**(participantId, title)\n→ get conversationId;
    :agent->**continue**(conversationId, participant);
  else (no — reuse existing conversation)
  endif
  :store->**storeUserMessage**\n<size:10>(conversation, participantId, prompt)</size>;
  :store->**storeAssistantMessage**\n<size:10>(conversation, participantId, prompt, response)</size>;
  :response->**withinConversation**\n<size:10>(conversation, participant)</size>;
else (no)
endif

|GeneratesText|
:Dispatch **AgentPrompted** event\n<size:10>(invocationId, processedPrompt, response)</size>;

:Return **AgentResponse** | **StructuredAgentResponse**;
stop

@enduml
